feat: v1.2 — 16 enhancements and bug fixes

New Features:
- Embedded cloudflared auto-download from GitHub Releases
- Auto-start Cloudflare Tunnel toggle
- Hide Dock icon option (menu bar only mode)
- Auto-update with one-click DMG download
- Error status code hints in request logs
- Export/save request logs as CSV
- Scrollable log list with 100-entry limit
- Enhanced glassmorphism animations

Bug Fixes:
- GitHub Actions CI tag pattern fix
- Unified button colors to theme accent
- Seamless transparent title bar
- Status bar left/right click handler fixed
- Fixed NSStatusItem.menu blocking action
- Fixed CloudflareTunnel stopSync race condition
- Fixed CSV export formatter and escaping

README:
- Added xattr fix for unsigned DMG
- Split into Chinese and English READMEs
- Fixed content errors
- Added real CI badge links
